title: Puma Ronnie Fieg x R698 'Sakura'  359620-01
description: Ronnie Fieg draws inspiration from his first trip to Tokyo for his latest Puma R698 'Sakura' sneaker. The shoe features a light pink base with white overlay panels and burgundy at the toe box, paying tribute to the city's famous annual cherry blossom festival. Other details include a petal-like scythed lateral formstripe, 3M KITH tongue branding, petal embroidery on its heel, and a tonal gradient fade on the Trinomic midsole. The Ronnie Fieg x Puma 'Tokyo Sakura Collection' also includes an RF698 Mid, both of which dropped in March 2015.
